        srcset="https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/ruiz-noncitizen-sentences-3x2_preview_maxWidth_3000_maxHeight_3000_ppi_72_embedColorProfile_true_quality_95_2025-09-03-215300_zeff.jpg?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=267&amp;q=75&amp;w=400&amp;s=70e5de01e98696c87280e175f199324e 400w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/ruiz-noncitizen-sentences-3x2_preview_maxWidth_3000_maxHeight_3000_ppi_72_embedColorProfile_true_quality_95_2025-09-03-215300_zeff.jpg?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=533&amp;q=75&amp;w=800&amp;s=0ae76278f900707f85f258bdf380c8f1 800w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/ruiz-noncitizen-sentences-3x2_preview_maxWidth_3000_maxHeight_3000_ppi_72_embedColorProfile_true_quality_95_2025-09-03-215300_zeff.jpg?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=800&amp;q=75&amp;w=1200&amp;s=ef13bf14453b3a93fc882a5f935aa513 1200w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/ruiz-noncitizen-sentences-3x2_preview_maxWidth_3000_maxHeight_3000_ppi_72_embedColorProfile_true_quality_95_2025-09-03-215300_zeff.jpg?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=867&amp;q=75&amp;w=1300&amp;s=aea2128abc33aca26fa9f70571ae4402 1300w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/ruiz-noncitizen-sentences-3x2_preview_maxWidth_3000_maxHeight_3000_ppi_72_embedColorProfile_true_quality_95_2025-09-03-215300_zeff.jpg?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=967&amp;q=75&amp;w=1450&amp;s=cccbd1641ba93a25dfeca3dabe96239c 1450w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/ruiz-noncitizen-sentences-3x2_preview_maxWidth_3000_maxHeight_3000_ppi_72_embedColorProfile_true_quality_95_2025-09-03-215300_zeff.jpg?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=1067&amp;q=75&amp;w=1600&amp;s=5b339a5b8126f6107c17337f0a573667 1600w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/ruiz-noncitizen-sentences-3x2_preview_maxWidth_3000_maxHeight_3000_ppi_72_embedColorProfile_true_quality_95_2025-09-03-215300_zeff.jpg?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=1333&amp;q=75&amp;w=2000&amp;s=65f5f8509ae646b0cb5ab36a214567f7 2000w"
                fetchpriority="high"    />


            
            
<figcaption class="attribution">
    
        <span class="attribution__credit">
        <span class="a11y">Credit: </span>
        Photo illustration by Shoshana Gordon/ProPublica. Source images: courtesy of Jorge Ruiz, obtained by ProPublica.
    </span>
    
    
    </figcaption>

        </figure>
            <div class="opener__topic-title-dek-wrapper">

                    <span class="opener__topics">
            <a class="opener__topics-link" href="https://www.propublica.org/topics/criminal-justice">Criminal Justice</a>
        </span>
    
    <h1
        class="opener__hed "
        
    >        The Complicated Case of Jorge Ruiz
    </h1>

    <h2
        class="opener__dek"
        style="display: none"        >
            A 19-year-old was arrested and charged with murder after a fatal car accident in Alabama. His lawyers have come to believe that one factor changed the course of the case, starting in the first moments after the crash.
    </h2>
    </div> <!-- Close .opener__topic-title-dek-wrapper -->

</div>
        
<div class="article-meta-1
     article-meta-1--left     " data-pp-location="article meta">

    <span class="article-meta-1__byline" data-pp-location="article byine">
