                    />

                </div>

    
<figcaption class="attribution">
        <span class="attribution__caption">First image: Ruiz, on the horse, grew up taking care of animals on his grandfather’s farm in rural Mexico. Second image: Ruiz, age 17, with his mom before she died suddenly in 2017.</span>
    
        <span class="attribution__credit">
